### 10.1 单元测试

```javascript
// 使用 Jest 或 Vitest
describe('Product API', () => {
  test('should get product list', async () => {
    const res = await request(app).get('/api/products')
    expect(res.status).toBe(200)
    expect(res.body.success).toBe(true)
